_header: A maiden mild hath born a child
_description: James Ryman, A Christmas carol — seven quatrains (abab) plus four-line burden (bbbb): ‘Bothe man & chielde haue myende of þis / How god is sonne of blis / Of Marie myelde man becomme is / To deye for mannys mys’

CULEe112.First Lines:
A mayden myelde hath born a chieldeA chielde of full grete
                    price…
CULEe112.Last Lines:
…That of a mayde man bicome isTo blis to bringe
                    mankyende
